{"post_payload": {"contentType": "article", "type": "article", "contentIdentity": "work", "title": "西湖亲子半日路线第一轮样本", "summary": "第一轮只覆盖了湖边步行和咖啡歇脚，还缺住宿与更完整的亲子视角。", "coverUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "tags": ["theme_city_walk", "scene_weekend_daytrip", "audience_family"], "locationName": "杭州西湖", "visibility": "public", "assistantUsePolicy": "inherit", "authorId": "fixture_user_travel", "authorDisplayNameSnapshot": "契约旅行家", "authorAvatarUrlSnapshot": "media/avatar/user/fixture_user_travel/v1/avatar.png", "sourceType": "cold_start_batch", "sourcePostId": "west_lake_crawl_validation_001_article_001", "articleDocument": {"template": "journal", "fontPreset": "clean", "coverImageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "titleStyle": "major", "nodes": [{"id": "title", "type": "documentTitle", "text": "西湖亲子半日路线第一轮样本"}, {"id": "paragraph_1", "type": "paragraph", "text": "这一轮只确定了西湖湖边和龙井路咖啡能串成一条半日路线。"}, {"id": "paragraph_2", "type": "paragraph", "text": "住宿与更完整的亲子叙事还需要下一轮继续补齐。"}, {"id": "figure_1", "type": "figure", "imageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "imageLayout": "fullWidth", "caption": "西湖半日漫游封面"}]}}, "semantic": {"entity_refs": ["trees/entities/地点/西湖.yaml", "trees/entities/本地生活/龙井路咖啡.yaml"], "tag_refs": ["trees/tags/主题/城市漫游.yaml", "trees/tags/场景/周末一日.yaml", "trees/tags/人群/亲子.yaml"], "source_urls": ["https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/west-lake-loop-round1"]}}
{"post_payload": {"contentType": "article", "type": "article", "contentIdentity": "work", "title": "补齐酒店回撤后的西湖亲子半日路线", "summary": "第二轮公开证据补齐了西湖边住宿与亲子回撤视角，让这条半日路线具备更完整的带娃可执行性。", "coverUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "tags": ["theme_city_walk", "scene_weekend_daytrip", "audience_family"], "locationName": "杭州西湖", "visibility": "public", "assistantUsePolicy": "inherit", "authorId": "fixture_user_travel", "authorDisplayNameSnapshot": "契约旅行家", "authorAvatarUrlSnapshot": "media/avatar/user/fixture_user_travel/v1/avatar.png", "sourceType": "cold_start_batch", "sourcePostId": "west_lake_crawl_validation_001_article_002", "articleDocument": {"template": "journal", "fontPreset": "clean", "coverImageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "titleStyle": "major", "nodes": [{"id": "title", "type": "documentTitle", "text": "补齐酒店回撤后的西湖亲子半日路线"}, {"id": "paragraph_1", "type": "paragraph", "text": "携程的亲子游记把杭州大华饭店列为住宿推荐，并强调它就在西湖边上，适合带孩子逛完湖边后尽快回撤休息。"}, {"id": "paragraph_2", "type": "paragraph", "text": "把西湖坐船、湖边步行、龙井路一带歇脚和西湖边住宿串起来后，这条路线已经不只是景点清单，而是更完整的亲子半日玩法。"}, {"id": "figure_1", "type": "figure", "imageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_crawl_validation_001/v1/cover.png", "imageLayout": "fullWidth", "caption": "西湖半日漫游封面"}]}}, "semantic": {"entity_refs": ["trees/entities/地点/西湖.yaml", "trees/entities/住宿/西湖亲子友好酒店.yaml", "trees/entities/本地生活/龙井路咖啡.yaml"], "tag_refs": ["trees/tags/主题/城市漫游.yaml", "trees/tags/场景/周末一日.yaml", "trees/tags/人群/亲子.yaml"], "source_urls": ["https://you.ctrip.com/travels/hangzhou14/4068300.html"]}}
